<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT16">
<l>nilaimaṉṉu meṉṉeñca mannāṉṟu tēvar</l>
<l>talaimaṉṉar tāmēmāṟ ṟāka palarmaṉṉar</l>
<l>pōrmāḷa veṅkatirōṉ māyap poḻilmaṟaiya</l>
<l>tērāḻi yālmaṟaittā rāl</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart will remain stable because of Him who hid the earth with the chariot wheel</l>
<l>so that it was hidden, as the sun vanished,</l>
<l>so that many kings died in battle</l>
<l>as the highest King of the gods Himself became [their] enemies on that day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
